e bend, but\nmulti-bend effects cannot be excluded entirely, and could play a role in high\nfrequency resonances. New simulation techniques have been developed, which\nshould be invaluable in further work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Feb 2015 23:22:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 May 2015 22:20:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
