gas density and CR energy density for use in galaxy-size or\ncosmological hydrodynamical simulations, and propose some key observational\ntests.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 Feb 2015 12:02:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Feb 2015 16:41:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
